UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`=' It can\'t be! After all this time, I thought it was lost forever. You thought this would amuse me? Do you think I long for a time before I was the queen of the Forsaken? Like you, it means nothing to me, and Alleria Windrunner is a long dead memory! You may now remove yourself from my presence, $C.' WHERE `word_id` = 272303; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9177
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='"Cookie" McWeaksauce at the Odesyus\' Landing wants you to bring him 6 Skittering Crawler Meat.' WHERE `word_id` = 272469; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=9512
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='"Shotgun" Jones wants you to speak with Hemet Nesingwary at the Nesingwary Safari on the outskirts of northeast Nagrand.' WHERE `word_id` = 272913; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10113
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$BExcellent. the warp rift generator is almost complete. There is only one final ingredient we require. Soon we shall be able to open up a warp rift to the deepest parts of the abyss. $B$BWho knows what strange creature may come through? Think of it $N. the power such knowledge will bring is limitless.' WHERE `word_id` = 150483; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10294
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$C, I need your help. In the Molten Core there are these stones, singed Corestones to be precise, that we need to harvest for the Ahn\'Qiraj war effort. I\'m told that our blacksmiths and engineers can put them to good use, so that\'s where you come in. I need you to go into the Molten Core and gather up as many of these corestones as you can. Of course, you\'ll want to talk thirty-nine of your closest friends along with you.' WHERE `word_id` = 146084; -- locales_quest - details : entry=8530
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$C, our sources tell us that the trolls buried in the Amani Catacombs inside Sungraze Peak have been rising from the dead. Dame Auriferous would have you investigate these catacombs and put to the torch any of the unanimated remains you come across so as to prevent any more of these creatures from rising.$B$BThe fastest way there is to head north out of town and then take the first fork to the right. This will put you on the north side of the peak, so look to the south for the entrance.' WHERE `word_id` = 146459; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9193
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$C, there\'s some tauren by the name of Thiah Redmane that keeps pestering us for assistance. She\'s with the Cenarion Expedition, and they\'ve setup a little post just to the west on the south side of the the road leading to Zangarmarsh.$B$BIf you hit Thornfang Hill, you\'ve gone too far.$B$BDo you think you might head over there and see what she needs?  I don\'t want to have to bother Ranger Captain Venn\'ren with such trivialities.' WHERE `word_id` = 151072; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10442
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$C, you must gather a group to investigate the Blood Furnace inside Hellfire Citadel at once!$B$BThe magical scrying that we have at our disposal indicates that something unnatural is occurring in there. But a powerful force inside is blocking any detailed arcane investigations, so it must be very important.$B$BYou should expect heavy resistance - no other mission that we\'ve sent in there has ever returned!$B$BScout it entirely and then report back to Nazgrel, advisor to Thrall, with what you witness.' WHERE `word_id` = 147680; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9608
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$G King : Queen; $N!  You speak with Mog\'dorg the Wizened before you leave and go to Ogri\'la!' WHERE `word_id` = 153342; -- locales_quest - details : entry=11022
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N - your name has passed my ears as one seeking out a master in the ways of the $C. You look capable enough, but I seek more than just looks from my students. You must be ready to delve where others fear to look to gain your power. I will teach you, but I will not tolerate failure.$B$BThere will be monetary costs associated with your training, but you should be more concerned with the cost your mind is willing to make. If you are ready, we shall begin.' WHERE `word_id` = 334914; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8563
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N! It is time for you to receive further training in the ways of the spirits. You should seek out Tuluun, the shaman at Azure Watch. He can begin your introduction to understanding and harnessing the power of flame.' WHERE `word_id` = 147099; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9462
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N! Or, should I say Junior Technician 1st Grade $N?! Oh hell, who am I kidding? Skipping a grade isn\'t a good enough reward for what you\'ve done. I\'m going to make you my first officer!$B$BYou\'ve saved all of us, and more importantly the X-52 Nether-Rocket! I could just kiss you... but I won\'t.$B$BInstead, please let me present you with the gratitude of Area 52. Take your pick!' WHERE `word_id` = 276261; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10249
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N! You bring joy to this old dwarf\'s heart.$B$BYou have now proven yourself; you\'ve joined the ranks of the elite! Others ran away in fear, or died, trampled under the foot of the beast. You used your mind, your cunning, your determination to prove your mastery of the hunt.$B$BTake this and know that you are always welcome to hunt at my side!' WHERE `word_id` = 148671; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9852
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, are you ready for another sortie over the Abyssal Shelf?  I fear that, if we do not maintain pressure on the legion forces there and allow them to strengthen their hold, then we may suffer a large demon attack from the north.$B$BWhat say you, $C?  Do you want to take another windrider and hammer the Abyssal Shelf one more time?' WHERE `word_id` = 150729; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10347
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, are your eyes keen as a hawk\'s, your motions as fluid as a monkey\'s, or your speed that of a cheetah?  Mine are, and yours can be too with the proper training. The way of the hunter is one of mastery over the beasts of the world, an unparalleled precision in marksmanship, and the knowledge of how to survive in situations where others would perish.$B$BIf these are the things that you seek to learn, then I will train you - for a small fee, of course. Shall we begin?' WHERE `word_id` = 272414; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9393
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, Farseer Nobundo has been asking for you. It must be time for you to learn the secrets of air, the last of the elements!$B$BI want you to know that I\'m very proud of all that you have accomplished thus far. I know that you have great things ahead of you.' WHERE `word_id` = 147430; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9547
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, I have a pet boar named Huffer. He wants to help you to have some fun with one of the nearby sons of Gruul.$B$BGrulloc inhabits a place known as the Cursed Hollow. When you get there, let Huffer loose. The gronn will have a fine time chasing him around, and you will retrieve the bag that he guards and deliver it to Baron Sablemane.$B$BTo get to the Cursed Hollow, head down the northern ramp and east through Dragons\' End. The hollow is on the eastern edge.' WHERE `word_id` = 152115; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10721
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, I have been expecting you.$B$BTullas has sung your praises and I am eager to continue your training on the path of Light. When you are ready to unlock greater understanding of your abilities and power, I will guide you.' WHERE `word_id` = 150768; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10366
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, I think that after you\'re done celebrating here, you should go back to the Cenarion Thicket and speak with Earthbinder Tavgren.$B$BI\'m certain that he\'ll want to know what really happened out there.' WHERE `word_id` = 149274; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10006
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, is it? I\'ve heard good things about you and the work you\'ve been doing in the short time since you came to.$B$BWe\'ll definitely need your help getting things back to normal. Zhanaa, over there, could also use your help, I\'m sure.' WHERE `word_id` = 150532; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10304
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, it falls to you to see that this attack by the Burning Legion never comes to pass. You must go and slay their leaders. Without them the rest of the demons are essentially mindless.$B$BYou will find Gorgannon in Demon Fall Canyon south beyond Felfire Hill, near Mannoroth\'s floating, broken spear.$B$BDiathorus the Seeker resides somewhere in the barrow den atop Demon Fall Ridge. To find the ridge, look for a ramp up from Demon Fall Canyon near the Horde\'s monument to Grom Hellscream.' WHERE `word_id` = 147323; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9522
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, it is good you are here. The Scourge attack our city with such endless hate that I fear the morale of our guard is breaking.$B$BHurry to the Dead Scar just south of the city where Jaela and her rangers stand ready. Fill them with the power of the Light through your blessings.' WHERE `word_id` = 147195; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9489
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, it is good you have come. Our list of allies grows thin, and even those who share our cause are not completely trusted. It is because of this that we, the rangers, turn to nature for aid.$B$BIn the allies of the forest we find a deep bond that does not know deceit.' WHERE `word_id` = 147704; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10529
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, now that you can see me, there is something you must tell Rexxar. I know that he seeks his people, and I know where they are.$B$BThe Mok\'Nathal, as they are known, have a village to the east beyond the Razor Ridge.$B$BGo, give Rexxar this news. His people are in danger, and I know that he will want to come to their aid.' WHERE `word_id` = 152099; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10718
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, once again Farseer Nobundo has been asking for you. It must be time for you to learn the secrets of air, the last of the elements!$B$BI want you to know that I\'m very proud of all that you have accomplished thus far. I know that you have great things ahead of you.$B$BTake the boat from Auberdine in Darkshore on Kalimdor. Cross the Veiled Sea and seek out the farseer inside the Crystal Hall of the Exodar on Azuremyst Isle.' WHERE `word_id` = 151242; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10491
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, one of our scouts has taken too strong an interest in his duties. He surveys our enemies relentlessly, but sends no reports of his findings.$B$BYou must find this spy, Keltus Darkleaf, convince him to hand over his report and return it to me as swiftly as possible. He can be found far to the southwest, where the Elrendar River forks and flows around Goldenmist Village. The night elves of An\'daroth are his quarry, and he won\'t be far from them.' WHERE `word_id` = 147373; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9532
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, we have reason to believe that the easternmost forge camp is not yet complete. The Legion\'s gan\'arg servants are working \'round the clock to get the facility up and running. We can\'t allow that to happen. $B$BHead east to Forge Camp: Mageddon and slay 10 gan\'arg. Bring me the head of their master - Razorsaw - and the Legion\'s fel reaver production will grind to a halt!   ' WHERE `word_id` = 273101; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10390
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, you have excelled in your early training and distinguished yourself among those who would become Blood Knights. You are ready to undertake the next phase of your training and, to that end, Knight-Lord Bloodvalor himself has asked to speak with you.$B$BI have no doubt that Knight-Lord Bloodvalor wishes to set a trial for you to test your abilities and training. You will find him in the Blood Knight headquarters in Silvermoon City\'s Farstriders\' Square. I wish you well, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 147906; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9677
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N, you will see to it that this attack by the Burning Legion never comes to pass!  Go and slay these dreadlords!  Without them the rest of the demons are essentially mindless.$B$BYou will find Gorgannon in Demon Fall Canyon south beyond Felfire Hill, near Mannoroth\'s floating, broken spear.$B$BDiathorus the Seeker resides somewhere in the barrow den atop Demon Fall Ridge. To find the ridge, look for a ramp up from Demon Fall Canyon near the monument to Grom Hellscream.' WHERE `word_id` = 147388; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9536
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$N. by my eternal soul, it is good to see you! I don\'t know why the Exodar crashed. Only those of us that were in this part of the ship remain.$B$BThere\'s not much time if we\'re to save everyone that we can!' WHERE `word_id` = 146587; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9279
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='$R fool. You almost destroyed the drum!$B$BI\'ve worked too hard to get here, and my hands have been empty up until now. At least you were able to succeed where the others only met with failure, or worse.$B$BIt is time to evoke a vision that will lead you to the last relic that I have been seeking.$B$BTake this fiery fragment of my soul. Use it to transform your body into flame and denature your spirit into a vision guide that will shoot forth to reveal the location of the final Thunderlord relic.' WHERE `word_id` = 151359; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10525
