UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Bomb parts. So my suspicions were true. That\'s not something that I wanted to be right about.$B$BOkay, you and I have some grim business ahead of us then.' WHERE `word_id` = 151081; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10444
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Bonechewers!  They should all die!  The sight of their red skin and depravity makes my blood boil!$B$BI have a mission for you, $N. Kill bonechewer orcs and collect their vile blood. There is an apothecary who needs the blood for her tests, so we can discover how these orcs fell to the demon taint, a taint from which we so recently freed ourselves.$B$BBonechewers scavenge near the ruined battlements along the Path of Glory, to the south. Return to me when your mission is complete.' WHERE `word_id` = 151104; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10450
