UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Dragonmaw treat you right, $N. Even a worn out cursed being like me is given a chance. Now if you want to prove your worth to the Skybreakers, you will have to defeat me.$B$BI\'m going to shake you off my tail like a bad case of fleas...$B$BWe\'ll lift off when you are ready.' WHERE `word_id` = 153523; -- locales_quest - details : entry=11067
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Drain Located' WHERE `word_id` = 148153; -- locales_quest - EndText : entry=9731
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Drazzit will expect to hear something from me soon, but I don\'t think the site is secure enough for me to leave. If you have time, would you be willing to take some of the salvaged cargo down to him at Mudsprocket?$B$BIf you haven\'t been there yet, it\'s a small settlement to the southwest of here, beyond the Stonemaul Ruins. You can take the road there from Tabetha\'s Farm, too. When you get to Mudsprocket, the guy you\'re looking for is Drazzit Dripvalve.' WHERE `word_id` = 154040; -- locales_quest - details : entry=11208
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Dreadlords!  They plan to attack us here at Splintertree Post?!$B$BNot while I still draw breath!$B$B<Valusha crumples the demon-scrawled plans in her fist.>$B$BNo. We will not allow this to happen!  They are a blight upon our world!' WHERE `word_id` = 147386; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9535
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Dugar\'s cargo doesn\'t seem to have been harmed or even opened. The cargo clearly seemed of interest to them, but it seems their prisoner was more important. What the arakkoa hoped to gain from attacking and kidnapping Dugar remains unclear, but the merchant is certainly not being held here. $B$BWithout any further clues as to how to continue your search, you decide it might be a good time to report your findings to Rokag.' WHERE `word_id` = 149054; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9947
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Durn\'s murderous grip has been loosed! Nagrand has a brighter tomorrow because of you, hero. Well done!' WHERE `word_id` = 149020; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9937
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Dwarfowitz at the Sha\'tari Base Camp in the Bone Wastes wants you to recover Enormous Bone Worm Organs.$B$BHe wants his Fumper back too.' WHERE `word_id` = 273563; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10930
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Each day, Hellfire Citadel opens its gates, and more fel orcs pour out and into the camps they\'ve established along the ramparts south of the fortress.$B$BI dispatched one of my most capable scouts, Private Imarion, to track their movements, preparations and numbers, but he hasn\'t returned to report his findings.$B$BImarion was to focus his efforts on the northernmost camp along the Southern Rampart, near where it joined the Citadel. Find him, $N. Without his information, we\'re sitting ducks.' WHERE `word_id` = 149737; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10122
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc4`='Each day, Hellfire Citadel opens its gates, and more fel orcs pour out and into the camps they\'ve established along the ramparts south of the fortress.$B$BI dispatched one of my most capable trackers, Scout Makha, to track their movements, preparations and numbers, but she hasn\'t returned to report her findings.$B$BMakha was to focus her efforts on the northernmost camp along the Northern Rampart, near where it ends in the rocks. Find her, $N. Without her information, we\'re sitting ducks.' WHERE `word_id` = 149848; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10150
